transcript:

Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Sir, Indiamart team se baat kar rahi hu.

Customer: Bolie.

Customer: Nahi nahi nahi.
Executive: Achha. Toh woh toh woh Facebook, Facebook, YouTube aur yeh Instagram mein woh link judega yeh mere ko bola tha.
Executive: Haan, main aapko bata deti hu. Abhi guide kar do kaise karna hai.
Customer: Nahi nahi mere aapka five days ho.
Executive: Actually sir, main aapko bata du aap aapke five days jab free honge toh main Prashant se call arrange kara dungi. Share chat mein aapko option aa raha hai. Waha pe aap share chat pe videos aap dal sakte hai.
Customer: [unintelligible] madam madam madam madam madam. Madam mere paas bhi main thoda busy hu aapka five days Prashant ko bol dijiye content ke liye.
Executive: Theek hai sir, theek hai. Okay, abhi koi concern nahi hai?
